<body class="gray-background">
    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center mt-5">
        <%= image_tag 'halalbytes-logo.png', style: 'width: 200px;'%>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center mt-5 mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-1 text-center mb-5">Welcome</h1>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <p class="lead text-center">Welcome to our website, dedicated to helping the Muslim community in Columbus, OH find halal spots to eat and share reviews. Discover a comprehensive database of halal restaurants, cafes, and eateries, complete with detailed information, ratings, and user reviews. Join our community and make informed dining choices while supporting halal preferences.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-3 text-center">
            <i class="bi bi-search h1 "></i>
            <p>Our search tool makes it easy to find and explore a variety of halal local restaurants, catering to your dietary needs. Discover delightful culinary gems and enjoy unforgettable dining experiences that meet your halal requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-1 text-center">
        </div>
        <div class="col-3 text-center">
            <i class="bi bi-star-half h1 "></i>
            <p>Join our community and contribute your valuable insights to help fellow diners find exceptional dining experiences. Your reviews have the power to guide others by sharing your thoughts on ambience, flavors, and attentive service, making a difference in their informed decision-making.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-1 text-center">
        </div>
        <div class="col-3 text-center">
            <%= image_tag 'mosque.png', style: 'width: 40px;' %>
            <p>Rest assured that all the restaurants in our database have undergone thorough verification to ensure they are halal-certified. Each establishment has been confirmed by either the owner or the company, giving you the confidence to explore and enjoy a diverse range of halal dining options with peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

<style>
  .gray-background {
    background-color:#DCDCDC; /* Replace with the desired shade of gray */
  }
</style>